quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  8,29,"Yemwe abemeye! Nimutinya Allah, azabashoboza gutandukanya ikibi n’icyiza,abahanagureho ibyaha byanyu ndetseanabababarire. Kandi Allah ni nyir’ingabire zihambaye"
  8,30,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo abahakanye bagucuriraga imigambi yo kugira ngo bakugire imbohe, cyangwa ngo bakwice, cyangwa ngo bakumeneshe. Bacuraga imigambi Allah akayiburizamo; kandi Allah ni we Uhebuje mu kuburizamo imigambi mibisha"
  8,31,"N’iyo basomewe amagambo yacu (Qur’an) baravuga bati \"Erega twarayumvise\"; n’iyo dushaka twari kuvuga ameze nka yo. Ibi nta cyo biri cyo usibye kuba ari inkuru z’abo hambere"
  8,32,"Unibuke (yewe Muhamadi) ubwo bavugaga bati \"Mana Nyagasani! Niba koko iyi (Qur’an) ari ukuri kuguturutseho, ngaho tugusheho imvura y’amabuye iturutse mu kirere, cyangwa utuzanire ibihano bibabaza"
  8,33,"Kandi Allah ntiyari kubahana mu gihe (wowe Muhamadi) ukibarimo, ndetse nta n’ubwo Allah yari kubahana mu gihe basaba imbabazi"
  8,34,"None se ni iki cyatuma Allah atabahana kandi bakumira (abantu) kugana umusigiti mutagatifu (Al Ka’abat), ndetse ntibabe n’abarinzi bawo? Nta bandi baba abarinzi bawo usibye abatinya Allah, nyamara abenshi muri bo ntibabizi"
  8,35,"Kandi amasengesho yabo ku musigiti mutagatifu (Al Ka’abat) yari ukuvugiriza no gukoma amashyi. Bityo, nimwumve ububabare kubera ibyo mwahakanaga. bw’ibihano"
  8,36,"Mu by’ukuri, babandi bahakanye batanga imitungo yabo kugira ngo bakumire (abantu) kugana inzira ya Allah. Bazanakomeza bayitange ariko iherezo bizabatera agahinda, maze batsindwe. Rwose abahakanye bazakoranyirizwa mu muriro wa Jahanamu"
  8,37,"Kugira ngo Allah atandukanye ababi n’abeza, agereke ababi ku bandi, maze abarundanye bose nuko abashyire mu muriro wa Jahanamu. Abo ni bo banyagihombo"